  "bodyText": "To ensure equitable access to quality education for all our citizens so that their potential is fully realized and also to assist in the development of responsible citizens who are disciplined, industrious, creative and confident and who can function effectively in a modern society.\n\n## Directory\n\n### Ministry of Educational Transformation\n\n| Role | Telephone |\n| --- | --- |\n| Secretary to the Permanent Secretary | (246) 535-0608 |\n\n### Higher Education Development Unit\n\n\"Anselm\" <br /> Government Hill <br /> St. Michael <br />\n\n| Role | Telephone |\n| --- | --- |\n| PBX | (246) 535-4050 |\n| Director | (246) 535-4051 |\n| Project Officer | (246) 535-4053 |\n| Information Technology | (246) 535-4056 |"
